Hi Team,
VSaaS is currently operating normally and scans are functioning as expected. The earlier failures were not due to a VSaaS outage, but were caused by an ongoing Artifactory federated binary instance performance issue.
Root Cause
Performance degradation in the Artifactory federated instance is delaying container image synchronization between primary and federated repositories.
Impact
Intermittent VSaaS scan failures occur when images are not yet synchronized or are delayed in propagation.
Status
VSaaS: Healthy
Artifactory Federation: Degraded (under investigation)
Next Steps
The Artifactory team is actively working to restore normal federation performance and reduce sync latency.
